v 3
d googlechart. Stata wrapper for the Google Charts (Visualization API)
d library.  Create a self-contained interactive HTML page, dashboard,
d or single embeddable iframe from any Stata dataset.
d
d Fourteen chart types: column, bar, line, area, combo, pie, donut,
d scatter, bubble, geo (country + US-state level), timeline, table
d (with built-in free-text search), histogram, divbar (Pew-style
d diverging stacked bar).  Native filter dropdowns via Google
d Dashboard + ControlWrapper.  Animation on most types.  Optional
d Texas 2036 brand palette + Montserrat typography via tx2036style.
d
d Self-contained -- no external Stata package dependencies.  The output
d HTML loads google.charts/loader.js from gstatic.com per Google ToS
d and therefore requires network access at view time.
d
d Requires: Stata 17+, network at view time for the resulting HTML.
d
d KW: google charts
d KW: visualization
d KW: interactive
d KW: html
d KW: dashboard
d KW: choropleth
d KW: divbar
d KW: likert
d
